1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,926
Pause and bring attention to your body.

2
00:00:08,926 --> 00:00:08,926
<break time="3s" />

3
00:00:08,926 --> 00:00:10,784
Start with your feet.

4
00:00:10,784 --> 00:00:14,499
Notice contact with the floor or surface
beneath you.

5
00:00:14,499 --> 00:00:15,706
Now notice your legs.

6
00:00:15,706 --> 00:00:16,495
Your hips.

7
00:00:16,495 --> 00:00:17,192
Your back.

8
00:00:17,192 --> 00:00:18,121
Your shoulders.

9
00:00:18,121 --> 00:00:18,864
Your jaw.

10
00:00:18,864 --> 00:00:20,164
Your face.

11
00:00:20,164 --> 00:00:22,254
You do not need to relax anything.

12
00:00:22,254 --> 00:00:23,183
Just notice.

13
00:00:23,183 --> 00:00:27,595
Now ask: Where is my body asking for
attention?

14
00:00:33,595 --> 00:00:33,595
<break time="3s" />

15
00:00:33,595 --> 00:00:36,103
Bring a little breath to that place.

16
00:00:36,103 --> 00:00:39,354
Ask: Is there a part connected to this
sensation?

17
00:00:45,354 --> 00:00:45,354
<break time="3s" />

18
00:00:45,354 --> 00:00:48,744
If yes, simply say: I notice you.

19
00:00:48,744 --> 00:00:51,252
If no, simply stay with the body.

20
00:00:51,252 --> 00:00:52,599
Take one slow breath in.

21
00:00:55,599 --> 00:00:56,621
And let it out.

22
00:00:56,621 --> 00:00:59,361
Return to the room with a little more
awareness.

